OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny residual
OL,6,Fshowers moving away southeastward this
OL,7,Fevening as clearer, dry conditions
OL,8,Ffollow from the northwest. Clear
OL,9,Fspells overnight giving a chilly start
OL,10,Fto Saturday, although cloud increasing
OL,11,Fagain from the west later. Breezy this
OL,12,Fevening but winds decreasing overnight.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FCloudy through the morning
OL,15,Fwith patchy light rain at times. Drier
OL,16,Fthrough the afternoon, with some
OL,17,Fbrighter spells. Winds strengthening
OL,18,Flater, strong inland, near gale along
OL,19,Fthe coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
